				<p class=""> <a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/bofm/alma/11.43?lang=spa#42" target="_blank">Alma 11:43</a>; v&eacute;ase tambi&eacute;n <a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/bofm/alma/40.23?lang=spa#22" target="_blank">Alma 40:23</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/ot/eccl/12.7?lang=spa#6" target="_blank">Eclesiast&eacute;s 12:7</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/138.17?lang=spa#16" target="_blank">D. y C. 138:17</a>.</p>
