				<p class=""> V&eacute;ase <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/89.18-21?lang=spa#17" target="_blank">Doctrina y Convenios 89:18–21</a>; v&eacute;ase tambi&eacute;n <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/rom/8.6?lang=spa#5" target="_blank">Romanos 8:6</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.38-39?lang=spa#37" target="_blank">2 Nefi 9:38–39</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.34-35?lang=spa#33" target="_blank">Doctrina y Convenios 29:34–35</a>.</p>
